f room and everything should be sitting pretty. Yeah... Just like that. It never felt so good to be right.\r\n\r\nAnd that''s a wrap, yo! You survived the tumultuous waters of alignment. Image alignment achievement unlocked!', 'КОНТАКТЫ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1080-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-11 15:18:56', '2017-01-11 12:18:56', '', 1080, 'http://goldiesgym.dev/1080-revision-v1.htm', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
